description: Welcome Dana DeArmond to US. Nicknamed the Jester for her nervous laugh as she is getting her ass kicked. The Goddess dominated this match from the start. However The Jester is determined to be a contender and vows to work hard to get there. She will have a long punishing road to travel, but I like her determination. Lets keep an eye on this one
title: The Goddess (Lifetime 7-4) vs The Jester (Lifetime 0-0)
